text: Tanja Slater (born 9 May 1978) is a road cyclist from United Kingdom. She represented her nation at the 2007 UCI Road World Championships. Slater is married and has a BSc Hons, Sport & Exercise Science. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1978 births Category:British female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
